through all the storms.

00:32:17,151 --> 00:32:24,057
And though enemies try
and stop the good news,

00:32:24,058 --> 00:32:28,895
Know that you have
much more backing you.

00:32:28,896 --> 00:32:33,066
So when you stand
in front of court officials,

00:32:33,067 --> 00:32:35,135
You are not alone.

00:32:35,136 --> 00:32:41,341
