00:33:15,543 --> 00:33:18,011
Please know you are.

00:33:22,684 --> 00:33:30,190
It is written:
‘You would suffer for the One you love’—

00:33:30,191 --> 00:33:34,127
Oh, the God you love.

00:33:34,128 --> 00:33:42,035
